div.p: Trigger: Invalid opcode, page fault, GPF, etc.

ul.li: Push SS, ESP, EFLAGS, CS, EIP to stack
Invalid IDT entry (selector not in GDT)
First exception handler causes another exception
Stack switch fails during first exception
IDT entry for first exception is invalid

div.p: CPU has no valid handler to invoke:

ul.li: No stack to push state to

ol.li: Valid IDT: All 256 entries must have valid handlers
Valid TSS: SS0:ESP0 must point to valid kernel stack
Kernel Stack Guard: Detect overflow before crash
Double Fault Handler: Must be bulletproof (use separate stack)
ISR Validation: Test all exception handlers
